attributes.title: Destiny 2 - Scouting Commander & Sentry Ranks x4 (Easter Egg)
attributes.caption: Learn how to find the secret scouting patrol easter egg on The Farm, max your sentry ranks, and get the Scouting Commander buff in Destiny 2.
attributes.description: Learn how to find the secret scouting patrol easter egg on The Farm, max your sentry ranks, and get the Scouting Commander buff in Destiny 2.Trevor teaches Geoff and Jack about a secret patrol mission on The Farm, Destiny 2's premiere social space. In this easter egg guide, learn how to nab the wheel boost and vertigo bonuses, max your sentry ranks, and earn the Commander's Blessing buff. Now you can super jump, run crazy fast, and look like Tron.
